- Org hierarchy rollout is additive: `.squad/config.json` stays at `version: 2` with `orgMode: false` as the safe default while `.squad/org/` artifacts and `dept:*` workflow metadata are prepared ahead of go-live.
- Active hierarchy routing surfaces are split across `.github/workflows/squad-triage.yml`, `.github/workflows/squad-issue-assign.yml`, and `sync-squad-labels.yml`; installed copies live under `.squad/templates/workflows/` and should stay in sync.
- Department truth is shared across `.squad/org/structure.json`, `.squad/team.md`, and `.squad/casting/registry.json`; validation should check those three together instead of only JSON syntax.
- The repo's local validation entry points are `validate-squad.js` and `validate-baseline.js`, but command execution is currently blocked in this environment because the available shell expects `pwsh.exe`.

